node.text: @tay.mk yah! he's at the height now where he is too tall for the smaller table and too short for the bigger table hahaa
@thattiredmom thanks for being with me on this one! I really tried to go with my plan but suddenly it's end of Apr hahahaha

We are coming to the end of HBL!!! 🥳. This was my first photo on the first day of HBL at 8am zzzzzzzz. .
I’m proud to share my original plan here (swipe) and report that NOTHING went according to plan 😂.
.
Swipe to see my daily workspace of nearly 12 hours a day...my kids’ room. I would do a workout while they have breakfast at ermmmm 10.30am? Then it’s HBL time and we would end up with a late lunch and yup, late dinner, and late bedtimes 😅. .
How are you all doing? Are you still keeping your kids to their usual bed time?.
.
.
.
#sgmummy #sgkids #sgunited #homebasedlearning #stayhomesg #letsgowedone #extendedcb29apr
@loveeveryday not really lol, but I have another for him to make sure he clears his daily assignments than to ask me what’s next.
@ngviv good job! Now holidays coming soon, another headache but at least more free-and-easy
3 months long holiday, Damien said “what so long” 😂😂
Haha more busy than normal days hor. I also did a timetable for Damien
@mynakedbar wow good job really on getting up at 7am and exercising too!
@loveeveryday 😋 tho short, the exercises really help to wake them up!! 😜

Nice schedule!! The bedtimes did stretch a little for us but I’m still dragging them up at 7am to do our morning exercise to get the oxygen pumping first thing in the morning! 😋 Happy last week of HBL!!
@chiabakann yes thanks for recognizing my efforts, I clean up every night and morning...😂
Very neat and clean space! Bravo 🎉🎉🎉
@appleohhh HBL ends May 4th, then no more assignments because MOE brought forward the June hols 😬. Yes I force myself to exercise no matter how off-schedule I am, it’s my must-do!!!
@loveeveryday Oh that’s for primary school, mine is in childcare so no hols. 🤣 wa mama power! 😱

@loveeveryday Are we? 😱 I thought there’s another month to go? 🤔 Wow mama u still got time to exercise for Mummy don’t even have any time left with my 2 kiddos around with juggling between WFH & HBL. 😅😂
@yukie.elurra yup this one looks like me but doesn’t behave like me 😂
Like mother like son!! 😂
@belandbray 30 mins daily! It’s my must-do. Esp now keep snacking sigh!!!!
Not bad leh, still can sneak in workout! The last I said I wanted to dig my mat out was 3 weeks ago 😆
@yilynnkee yes it is! the kids usually hang out in the living room, we only use these tables when we have to
The built-in study table is such a smart idea!
@enegue_aol i am doing the HBL too hahaha
You look like the one HBL
Well organised
@thadlin thanks haha
@thadlin thanks haha
@thadlin thanks haha
@aliciacho yup! saves space! we only use it when we have to, they usually do their homework in the living room but now living room taken up by daddy
Matt’s table so cool!! Can push in and out. I’m counting down to next Monday. Hang in there! It’s not easy...
@tay.mk yah! he's at the height now where he is too tall for the smaller table and too short for the bigger table hahaa
The study table is such a good idea though too high for him. The room is so neat and clean
Very well organised
@thattiredmom thanks for being with me on this one! I really tried to go with my plan but suddenly it's end of Apr hahahaha
Hey hi-5 nothing went according to plan in our house too 😂
